         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">16/4/94. ¶  ¶ This evening, dear Mr Macdonald, I received your kind letter of this day, ¶ Letter not found. ¶  ¶ and in answer I support your view, that a sum of £10 or more be voted for the children ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">94.04.16</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Alexander Macdonald</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A38, The Royal Geographical Society of Australasia (Victorian Branch), Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">16/4/94.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This evening, dear Mr Macdonald, I received your kind letter of this day,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and in answer I support your view, that a sum of £10 or more be voted for the children of Mr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #000000; ">Le Mestre</seg>,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>La<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Meslée?<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Edmond Marin La Meslée and his wife were drowned when the pleasure-boat<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Ripple</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>capsized in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sydney Harbour in December 1893,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>being survided by three sons<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">ADB</seg>). A fund was established to support the orphans (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Sydney morning herald</seg>, 12 January 1894, p. 4).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>all the more so as their father gave really the first impulse to the formation of the RGSA and worked for a year or two strenuously for it, til he came into antagonism to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sir Strickland.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir Edward Strickland.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Thursday afternoon I will make free for a Council meeting. Perhaps you could ascertain before, whether Mr Turner<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Henry Gyles Turner.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>will or can make free £10 (or more) from our locked up fund for this appealing purpose.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Please return your kind brothers letter, as I have not yet replied. Yesterday I sent your brother, the Police-Magistrate<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>John Graham Macdonald (1834-1918), Queensland Police Magistrate from 1872 (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Brisbane courier</seg>, 30 May 1918, p. 9). In 1894<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>he was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>based in Townsville (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">The week</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Brisbane), 20 April 1894, p. 24).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>one of my book.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I write in great hurry amidst mail-work</p>
         </div>
      </body>
